## Usage Example

Here's a basic usage example of the `SidebarToggle`:

```tsx
<Canvas>
  <Story name="Default">
    <SidebarToggle
      collapsed={false}
      onClick={() => console.info("Toggle sidebar")}
      className="mb-4"
    />
  </Story>
</Canvas>
``` 